snippet.textDisplay: You should put ion ‘sapphire’ and/or ‘tanzanite’ color from Sally’s beauty in your hair. Keep your dark color but add those two colors throughout your hair. It would give it some really cool dimension. The tanzanite seems super purple but it’s actually more of an indigo. I just think that would look so good on you! It’s semi permanent so it would wash out after awhile and you don’t have to fully lighten your hair that much for the colors to show up. Arctic fox ‘beach, please’ is a really good bleach that won’t damage your hair too bad. Obviously find a hairdresser to do all this. If I lived in LA I would totally do it for you but I’m in Fort Worth Texas.
